OL,3,CWho is Slovakian Prime Minister Robert
OL,4,CFico?
OL,6,FWords by Hannah Norbury
OL,8,FSlovakian Prime Minister Robert Fico,
OL,9,F59, is in serious but stable condition
OL,10,Fafter he was on Wednesday.
OL,12,FHe had been greeting supporters at an
OL,13,Fevent in the town of Handlova, nearly
OL,14,F140 kilometres northeast of the
OL,15,Fcapital, when he was attacked. A total
OL,16,Fof five shots were fired.
OL,18,FThe attacker has not yet been named,
OL,19,Fbut was described as a 71-year-old
OL,20,Ffrom the town of Levice. He was
OL,21,Fcharged on Thursday.
