OL,3,CWho is Slovakian Prime Minister Robert
OL,4,CFico?
OL,6,FThe attempt on Fico's life also came
OL,7,Fat a time of high division in
OL,8,FSlovakia, as thousands of
OL,9,Fdemonstrators have repeatedly rallied
OL,10,Fin the capital and around the country
OL,11,Fto protest his pro-Russian, anti-
OL,12,FAmerican messages.
OL,14,FIt also comes just ahead of June
OL,15,Felections for the European Parliament.
OL,17,FBut who is Fico, and why is he such a
OL,18,Fdivisive figure in Slovakia? ITV News
OL,19,Fexplains.
