OL,3,CWho is Slovakian Prime Minister Robert
OL,4,CFico?
OL,6,FBorn in 1964 - in what was then
OL,7,FCzechoslovakia - Fico began his
OL,8,Fpolitical journey as a member of the
OL,9,FCommunist Party.
OL,11,FIn the late 1990s, he founded the Smer
OL,12,Fparty, becoming its chairman in 1999.
OL,14,FThe party was once described as left-
OL,15,Fpopulist, but has over the last years,
OL,16,Fembraced right-wing views on
OL,17,Fimmigration and cultural issues.
OL,19,FMost recently, Fico was compared to
OL,20,Fthe nationalist prime minister of
OL,21,Fneighboring Hungary, Viktor Orban.
