OL,3,CWho is Slovakian Prime Minister Robert
OL,4,CFico?
OL,6,FFico began the first of his three
OL,7,Fterms as prime minister in 2006,
OL,8,Fserving for four years before going
OL,9,Finto opposition after his coalition
OL,10,Flost an election.
OL,12,FHe returned to power in 2012 but
OL,13,Fresigned as prime minister in July
OL,14,F2018 following mass demonstrations
OL,15,Fover the murder of journalist Jan
OL,16,FKuciak and his fiancee.
OL,18,FKuciak had been reporting on tax-
OL,19,Frelated crimes implicating politicians
OL,20,Fin Fico's party, and his murder set
OL,21,Foff a political crisis for Fico.
