OL,6,FIn one infamous press conference, Fico
OL,7,Fwas pictures with bundles of cash on a
OL,8,Ftable, promising to pay E1 million for
OL,9,Finformation leading to the capture of
OL,10,Fthe killer.
OL,12,FDespite being temporarily ousted, Fico
OL,13,Fwas re-elected for a third term last
OL,14,Fyear, with his party winning the
